title: French police clash with eco-activists at abandoned airport site
text:
French police clash with eco-activists at abandoned airport site Monday, April 09, 2018 - 00:45 
French police clear eco-activists using tear gas and stun grenades from a site in western France that had been planned as a new airport. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
